name: Epic Trance
description_short: Trance in its most boisterous form. Uplifting melodies on top of high energy beats create these euphoric anthems.

name: Deep Progressive Trance
description_short: A subgenre of Progressive Trance that features a deeper, more emotional and melodic sound.

name: Oldschool Acid
description_short: Acid, one of the characteristics of the TB-303, is celebrated here with the best tracks from house, techno and trance.

name: Chillout
description_short: Electronic sounds, mellow mid-tempo rhythms, and a groove meant to calm the senses and ease the mind.

name: Dark PsyTrance
description_short: The darker form of PsyTrance, which is a sound all its own – direct from Goa to your headphones.

name: Deep House
description_short: House music crafted for the smaller and mid-sized rooms - deeper tracks full of silky, smooth grooves.

name: Oldschool House
description_short: The biggest classics and secret weapons – this is a true treasure chest of house tracks from back in the day.

name: House
description_short: Born in Chicago and now global, house music is always evolving but remains true to its pure 4/4 structure.

name: Classic EuroDisco
description_short: Conceived in the European discos  in the 70s, evolving through the decades into modern electronic masterpieces.

name: Dub Techno
description_short: The beloved sounds of deep techno saturated with tape delays, heavy reverb and ice cold atmospherics.

name: Dub
description_short: An emphasis on the bass and drums / DnB, delayed effects, sampled vocals and smokey Reggae inspired vibes.

name: Gabber
description_short: The hardest form of techno with punishing tracks designed to drive the crowds into a sweaty frenzy.

name: Minimal
description_short: Minimal fuses elements of house, techno and electronica and strips it back to focus on the spaces between the sound.

name: New Age
description_short: Slow, soothing and open-minded music for relaxing, thinking, and enjoying.

name: Trance
description_short: Emotive dance music which embraces incredible melodies, future-facing production and energetic anthems heard worldwide.

name: Techno
description_short: Techno is a true musical force full of structure and style. Robotic, mechanical and full of soul, always facing the future.

name: Classic Trance
description_short: The classic melodies, the epic breakdowns and gigantic builds. Re-experience Trance music in her prime.

name: Progressive Psy
description_short: Progress your mind to undiscovered psychedelic dimensions.

name: Chillstep
description_short: The brilliant combination of dubstep rhythms with the mellow grooves of chillout. A unique sound all its own.

name: Hard Techno
description_short: Tough as nails warehouse jams full of cold aggression, sinister structures and pounding rhythms that hit hard.

name: Underground Techno
description_short: From gritty Berlin streets to dark corners of Brooklyn, this is techno made by artists pushing the genre further.
